WEBVTT

00:02.410 --> 00:05.913
Okay, folks... show is over!

00:06.372 --> 00:10.375
It's time for Elvis
to leave the building.

00:10.687 --> 00:12.638
It's a long way down, friend.

00:12.871 --> 00:14.906
Oh.

00:16.856 --> 00:18.714
Who are you?

00:18.478 --> 00:20.446
Where the hell
did you come from?

00:20.513 --> 00:22.381
That doesn't matter.

00:22.449 --> 00:24.383
What matters
is you.

00:26.453 --> 00:28.520
Do you understand
you are about to embark

00:28.588 --> 00:30.756
on a course of action
from which there is

00:30.824 --> 00:32.825
no turning back?

00:33.927 --> 00:36.061
Oh, such a waste!

00:36.129 --> 00:39.498
You're so young,
so filled with promise.

00:41.201 --> 00:43.469
Promise?

00:43.520 --> 00:46.872
In the last two weeks,
I've lost my job,

00:46.940 --> 00:50.476
I lost my apartment,
lost a fight...

00:50.543 --> 00:53.579
So if it's promise
that you're looking for...

00:56.549 --> 01:00.286
I think you may have me
confused with someone else.

01:05.025 --> 01:06.625
Michael...

01:06.693 --> 01:08.027
I can help you.

01:08.094 --> 01:10.429
I can show you how to
turn your life around.

01:10.497 --> 01:12.665
How'd you do that?

01:12.732 --> 01:16.769
Weren't you just over there?

01:16.836 --> 01:19.838
And how'd you
know my name?

01:19.906 --> 01:23.776
I know everything.

01:23.843 --> 01:25.644
I can see
everything.

01:27.414 --> 01:30.115
Come on, Michael,
say yes.

01:30.183 --> 01:33.052
Say yes to me.
Say yes to success.

01:34.187 --> 01:36.789
Yes to success.

01:36.856 --> 01:40.960
Wow. If it was
only that easy.

01:41.027 --> 01:42.461
But it is.

01:42.529 --> 01:44.463
Come on!

01:44.531 --> 01:46.465
Look at yourself.

01:46.533 --> 01:48.367
What have you got to lose?

01:51.871 --> 01:54.273
Sure.

01:54.341 --> 01:55.874
Absolutely!

01:55.942 --> 01:58.744
Yes!

