Everything okay?

02:10.889 --> 02:15.561
Yeah.
Just had a horrible dream.

02:15.612 --> 02:17.429
My brother Michael.

02:17.497 --> 02:19.531
I'm worried; I think
he might be in trouble.

02:19.599 --> 02:21.900
You needed a dream
to tell you that?

